snippet.title: Final Factory Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST NOW: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1383150/Final_Factory/?utm_source=atrailer

DISCORD for playtesting steam keys: https://discord.gg/78JaMfPkhX

Final Factory blends factory building with a rich universe to explore. Build a vast network of automated space stations and command a massive fleet against the hostile local aliens. Discover new technologies and unlock the secrets of an ancient civilization as you explore an infinite cosmos. 

Original Score and game soundtrack by Zayn Mufti https://www.zaynmuftimusic.com/
